CAD Courses

Fundamental Courses

Civil CADD

Learn skills in analyzing & calculating the rigidity, stability, and strength of structures, land survey & transportation design, and building design.

Enroll Now

Mechanical CADD

Design, analyze, and manufacture mechanical tools, engines, and machines to increase productivity and achieve greater speed and efficiency of work.

Enroll Now

Electrical CADD

Utilize this resourceful course to design electrical equipment and electronic products – from microchips & computers to electric power networks and many more.

Enroll Now

Electronic CADD

Create and modify circuits, present graphical representations of electronic components and interconnections, circuit simulation, etc with a dedicated electronics program.

Enroll Now

Architectural CADD

Compile layouts, design conceptual elements, components, and systems like interior partitions, floor finishes, and entire design drawings with Architectural CAD training.

Enroll Now

Project Management

Learn to administer and manage the projects by gaining insights on the project lifecycles, initiate structured planning with resourceful project tools and techniques, and many more.

Enroll Now

Advanced Courses

Revit- Architecture

Create more accurate and optimized designs. Use Revit building design software for every phase of your project, from concept to visualization, and complete your work efficiently.

Enroll Now

3DS max

A rich and flexible toolset to create premium designs with full artistic control. Model finely detailed interiors and objects. Bring characters and features to life with animation and VFX.

Enroll Now

STAAD Pro

STAAD Pro Software – a structural analysis and design software application to perform comprehensive analysis and design for any size or type of structure faster than ever before.

Enroll Now

Primavera

An enterprise project portfolio management software that helps to do project management, risk analysis, resource management, collaboration, and control capabilities, and integrates with other enterprise softwares.

Enroll Now

ETABS

An engineering software used for the analysis of concrete shear walls and concrete moment frames. Highly acclaimed for static and dynamic analysis of multi-storey wall buildings.

Enroll Now

BIM-MEP

Design, detail, and document building systems more efficiently with this intelligent, 3D model-based process that gives more insight into designs and constructability, and improves outcomes.

Enroll Now

Catia

Develop and improve product designs with this multi-platform software suite used for computer-aided design, computer-aided manufacturing, computer-aided engineering.

Enroll Now

Pro E

Learn this multi-program software that can be used for designing, analysising, and manufacturing. It deals with the model creation and assembly of designs.

Enroll Now

Solidworks

Develop mechatronic systems from beginning to end by using this solid modeling software. Design & build mechanical, electrical, and many more useful software elements by learning it.

Enroll Now

Real Projects

Mining works

Get to work on some of the industry-based projects in the mining industry and develop an experience that adds to your portfolio. Upgrade your skillset to a job-ready position with this course.

Enroll Now

Building Plans

 Build some of the finest executive plans, develop them by getting to work on some of the industry-based projects. Upgrade your skillset to a job-ready position with this course.

Enroll Now

Municipality
Plans and Layouts

Learn to work on Municipal plans and layout projects by gaining insights into the municipality industry through all the helpful resources and gain an experience that adds to your profile.

Enroll Now

Canal works

Learn to work on Canal Projects of our state and country by gaining insights into the canal industry through the help of supportive trainers and resources associated with our course.

Enroll Now

Structural Designs

Compile layouts and structural designings with the real-time project opportunities and prepare yourself for a thriving career in the architectural and designing career fields.

Enroll Now

Elevations and Designs

Explore the best new designs for elevation by the hands-on project opportunity and gain useful insights and experiential learnings in the field. Add value to your profile with this useful project.

Enroll Now
